This project (Quotation Automation System) deploys to **ONE** VPS:

| Detail | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Public IP** | `165.22.110.111` |
| **Tailscale IP** | `100.86.182.7` |
| **SSH User** | `root` |
| **SSH Key** | `~/.ssh/id_ed25519_roo` |
